-- Stocks in Switzerland Advance, Led by Shares of Credit Suisse, Nestle, ABB
-- B y   S r i n i v a s a n   S i v a b a l a n
-- 2012-02-28T08:37:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-28/stocks-in-switzerland-advance-led-by-shares-of-credit-suisse-nestle-abb.html
 Swiss stocks advanced, snapping two
days of declines, as shares of Credit Suisse Group AG, UBS AG,
ABB Ltd. and Nestle SA gained.  The benchmark Swiss Market Index rose 0.4 percent to
6,167.85 at 9:36 a.m. in Zurich.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
